ResumeBytes Copilot Extension makes your job search easier by automating application inputs and customizing right from the job post. With just one click, autofill job applications and generate resumes tailored to job descriptions using your unique voice, all powered by ChatGPT 4 or o1. Whether you're applying through Lever, Greenhouse, Workday, or nearly any other job platform, ResumeBytes simplifies the job search process.

Breeze through job applications without the repetitive input, create cover letters, and answer lengthy prompts instantly using AI to ensure your responses are personalized and relevant to each role. Your applications are automatically cataloged and searchable in your dashboard, making your job search more manageable and efficent.
